 US Army Staf Sgt Julian McDonald , welcomed 4-year-old Layka , a Belgian Malinois , into his Columbus , Ohio home after fighting to adopt her for two years .
Layka was on her eighth overseas military tour with Sgt.
McDonald in 2012 when she was shot four times at point blank range by an enemy fighter armed with an AK-47 .
Despite being injured , Layka and McDonald 's son Liam have become best friends .